{"article_id":"ZA0xXTdBz7zPi5zr","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"House Democratic leaders on Wednesday said","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"they were not in a rush","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to hand off impeachment to the Senate ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"demanding a fair process .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"\" The question is now whether Senator McConnell will allow a fair trial in the Senate , \"","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"House Permanent Select Committee on Intelligence Chairman Adam B. Schiff said .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"\" A trial","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that should be fair to the president , yes ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"but should be fair also to the American people . \"","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi said","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"the next step for the House","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"- naming impeachment managers -","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"can not occur","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"until they know","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"what the process will look like in the next chamber .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"It ' s unclear how long Democrats will hold the articles in the House .","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"\" We can not name managers","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"until we see what the process is on the Senate side . ...","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"So far , we haven ' t seen anything","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"that looks fair to us , \"","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"the California Democrat said .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"A delay","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"in sending the articles of impeachment to the Senate","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"raises a host of questions .","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"The House has the power","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"to impeach ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"but it takes a Senate trial","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"to convict and remove a president from office .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"It was unclear how , or even whether , a delay would pressure the Senate to adopt Democrat-friendly procedures for a trial .","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"The move also appeared to run afoul of the Constitution","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Mrs. Pelosi , California Democrat , said","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"she was protecting","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"when pushing through the impeachment of Mr. Trump .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"The Constitution says","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"the Senate \" shall have the sole power","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"to try all impeachments . \"","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"While House Democrats wouldn ' t detail all of their criteria","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"for how the Senate proceedings should unfold ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"Mrs. Pelosi said","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"it ' s not a fair process right now","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"as Majority Leader Mitch McConnell is coordinating and \" in cahoots \" with the White House .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Both President Trump and Senate Minority Leader Charles E. Schumer have called for an extended trial with witnesses","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"called to testify ,","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"but Mr. McConnell and Senate Judiciary Committee Lindsey Graham prefer to have a streamlined process .","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"The comments from Mrs. Pelosi and her committee chairs came","depth":3},{"id":46,"text":"immediately","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"after Democrats voted to impeach the president on charges of abuse of power and obstruction of Congress .","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"\" I could not be more proud or more inspired by the moral courage of House Democrats .","depth":4},{"id":49,"text":"We never asked one of them how they were going to vote .","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"We never whipped this vote , \"","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"the speaker said .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":103,"left":96,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":72,"right":95,"relation":"elaboration","nuc